children.text: The page was manually generated to compare two video events: Bobby Pickett on American Bandstand (1964) and Bobby Pickett on New York at Night (1991). The two can be compared based on the same performer, Bobby Pickett, and the contrasting years of the performances (1991 vs. 1964).

The following comparison of Bobby Pickett's performances of the "Monster Mash" will feature important themes of how the "Monster Mash" has maintained between the 33 years of these two performance. This will include annotations of the differences and continuations of the "Monster Mash" in '94 visually, sonically, and performance-wise from what it was initially in '64.

title: Comparison clips - multiple video events + annotations
